Package: simple-backup
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Build-Depends: g++, nlohmann-json3-dev
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libstdc++6
Maintainer: Simple Backup <admin@example.com>
Description: Simple inotify-based directory backup service
 Watches configured source directories for changes using the Linux
 inotify API and copies modified files to a configured output location.
 Uses signalfd + poll(2) so the process sleeps with zero CPU when idle.
